Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,==========TEXT==========
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.69,0:03:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓到0號了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.74,0:03:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在Arachne正在追擊中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.74,0:03:52.73,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arachne：希臘神話中的紡織高手 挑戰雅典娜失敗 下場很悲劇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.54,0:03:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cyclopes需要進行再調整
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.54,0:03:56.65,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cyclopes：希臘神話中的獨眼巨人 X戰警的隊長 某某高達中某某基地下面的自爆裝置等等都引用於此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.74,0:03:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.27,0:04:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為原石品質的低劣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.43,0:04:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給外部帶來了影響
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.52,0:04:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.78,0:04:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要比現在的等級更高的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.90,0:04:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有他們的東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.12,0:04:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 還沒有那個必要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.30,0:04:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.72,0:04:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到治療的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不注射這種藥的話 你就會變成怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.49,0:05:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然因為副作用會有點痛 不過你就忍忍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.06,0:05:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼請開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.45,0:05:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.19,0:05:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.95,0:05:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.36,0:05:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從我身上提取出來的血清
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.94,0:06:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有什麼太大的效果
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.94,0:06:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳再這樣亂來會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.68,0:06:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果沒有血清的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.13,0:06:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈特就會變成真正的惡石
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.43,0:06:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,製造濃度更高的血清
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.91,0:06:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從藍羽…瑠璃身上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.85,0:06:27.41,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天從課本185頁開始
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.43,0:06:34.28,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是關於上節課裡被稱為現代經濟史一環的國富論
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.77,0:06:38.54,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國富論就如上節課所教的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.85,0:06:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手裡劍？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.35,0:06:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏡？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.65,0:06:40.10,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是由亞當·斯密所著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:43.01,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對現代社會的經濟史產生了巨大影響的一本書
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.69,0:06:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午休時能一起吃便當嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.10,0:06:46.85,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最有名的是「無形的手」這一概念
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.65,0:06:56.16,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞當·斯密認為人們就算自由地進行生產活動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.08,0:06:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.55,0:07:04.24,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社會不僅不會陷入混亂 反而會走上和諧繁榮的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.92,0:07:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也做了阿爾瑪同學的那份  瑠璃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.43,0:07:07.85,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後課本的186頁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.94,0:07:12.83,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,則是亞當·斯密闡述其中政府的職責充其量就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.39,0:07:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.14,0:07:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹童子同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.91,0:07:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去一下洗手間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.25,0:07:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢…慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.88,0:07:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.54,0:07:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來想叫你一聲的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.29,0:07:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過看你還在睡覺就…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.10,0:07:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很擔心你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.96,0:07:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你一直沒回教室
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.97,0:07:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.29,0:08:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微…什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.01,0:08:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好近！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.57,0:08:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳…總是靠得很近啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.07,0:08:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離…我們倆說話時候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.31,0:08:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.95,0:08:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我說話的時候 能不能保持1米的距離啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.80,0:08:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 阿爾瑪同學果然還是喜歡一個人獨處嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.80,0:08:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不是 也不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.01,0:08:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是還沒習慣這種樣子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.33,0:08:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼要不要特訓一下啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.81,0:08:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如我就這樣住進阿爾瑪同學的家裡之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.40,0:08:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.66,0:08:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就一個人吃便當吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.22,0:08:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.38,0:08:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你無所謂嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.57,0:08:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我吃掉兩人份的便當然後變胖也無所謂？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.28,0:08:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…真是麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.39,0:08:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩？是在說我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.09,0:08:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 我不是那個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.93,0:09:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 那我去別的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.41,0:09:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.37,0:09:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…真的走了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.03,0:09:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…或許真的有點煩人啊

Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.66,0:09:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳變成大美人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:09:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得 像這樣一直打磨石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.05,0:10:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種邁入老年的感覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.79,0:10:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊 就好像一邊喝著粗茶 一邊坐在走廊上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.86,0:10:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想將來…你說對吧 鏡同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.95,0:10:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 妳在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.07,0:10:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為一起坐著的肯定是我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.84,0:10:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 鏡同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.10,0:10:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 鏡同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.95,0:10:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.56,0:10:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有非常麻煩的微笑湊過來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.50,0:10:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.54,0:10:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐 石頭的打磨這樣就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.61,0:10:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.20,0:10:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.77,0:10:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有些心事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.71,0:10:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了鏡同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.99,0:10:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不懂怎麼打磨嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.51,0:10:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如果說一聲的話 我明明就會來教你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.36,0:10:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.97,0:11:07.22,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 你到底在裝什麼內行啊 我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.87,0:11:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 丹童子同學沒有來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.85,0:11:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.74,0:11:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹童子同學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.51,0:11:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為個子太高
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.89,0:11:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一不在的話 感覺就像是沒有了大佛的鐮倉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.54,0:11:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.08,0:11:18.63,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也沒打磨到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.68,0:11:20.90,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 早就打磨到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:22.52,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒打磨到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.57,0:11:23.82,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部長妳不擔心他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.58,0:11:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擔心什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.04,0:11:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹童子同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.94,0:11:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 每個人都有自己的事情要忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.94,0:11:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過分干涉也不太好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.66,0:11:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許又去河邊撿石頭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.77,0:11:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊 我很煩人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.46,0:11:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐 時間差不多到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.38,0:11:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,財團的例行理事會議
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.40,0:11:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經都這時候了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.67,0:11:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏡同學已經要回去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.30,0:11:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非…非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.13,0:11:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.02,0:11:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也沒辦法啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:12:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我們就先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.62,0:12:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.79,0:12:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說若菜啊 既然鏡同學已經回去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.70,0:12:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直截了當的說 我們可以回去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.25,0:12:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.29,0:12:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話 今天多虧了有理事會議才得救啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.35,0:12:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 只是一味打磨石頭的工作真讓人受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.96,0:12:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說這世上有很多事情讓人無法忍受
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.84,0:12:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只有那個 都能讓我開始懷疑自己生存的意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.54,0:12:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然能讓你大肆抱怨 看來極其麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.94,0:12:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個實在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.11,0:12:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,極其讓人受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.91,0:12:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.41,0:12:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是一個很麻煩的女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.24,0:12:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.44,0:13:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我差點就要碎了啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.84,0:13:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.85,0:13:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 只是稍微擦到了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.28,0:13:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有哪裡覺得痛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.49,0:13:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.04,0:13:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上去醫院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.84,0:13:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用 我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.37,0:13:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑠璃 瑠璃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.43,0:13:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有惡石的氣息啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.51,0:13:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要對瑠璃做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.23,0:13:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.21,0:13:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然就跳出來 真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.82,0:13:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓您費心了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.77,0:13:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說妳 真傷腦筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.53,0:13:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.04,0:13:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒事的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.10,0:13:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.91,0:14:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐 大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.98,0:14:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.17,0:14:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快找到大小姐在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.97,0:14:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩位沒有在一起嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.82,0:14:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一不留神她就消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.93,0:14:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在大小姐的手機沒有訊號
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.83,0:14:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GPS以及各感應器都沒有反應
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.34,0:14:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.26,0:14:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯絡區縣警署
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.95,0:14:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要求緊急搜查
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.97,0:14:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.85,0:14:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.30,0:14:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研美先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.55,0:14:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.89,0:14:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍羽瑠璃失蹤了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.29,0:14:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑠璃醬她？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.91,0:14:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是輝島奈特嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.31,0:14:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.91,0:14:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能出動Cyclopes嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.51,0:14:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在調整中…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:14:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.66,0:15:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是您身體狀況也不太好…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.85,0:15:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢貨！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.27,0:15:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍羽財團陷入危機
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.75,0:15:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我不出動的話還有誰會出動？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.01,0:15:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果奈特拐走了瑠璃醬的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.64,0:15:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他下一個接觸對象一定就是丹童子君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.71,0:15:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.17,0:15:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就看準這點出擊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.74,0:15:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arachne能出動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.58,0:15:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.28,0:15:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳也會來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.10,0:15:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.15,0:15:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹童子 大小姐失蹤了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.13,0:15:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.46,0:15:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.16,0:15:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.47,0:15:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.55,0:15:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.22,0:15:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.15,0:15:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一瞬間就消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.80,0:16:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道 就在我稍微下車的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.03,0:16:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手機呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.33,0:16:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接不通
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.59,0:16:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏡先生 搜查的準備做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.65,0:16:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 我馬上過來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.42,0:16:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.93,0:16:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就別來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.41,0:16:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是和惡石有關的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.63,0:16:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你過來只能成為累贅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.05,0:16:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有什麼事的話我會聯絡你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.05,0:16:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.48,0:16:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是不是看到了什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.60,0:16:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 我去別的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.95,0:16:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她不在了我會怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.68,0:17:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成惡石的話不就無法恢復了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.07,0:17:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊我！只考慮自己的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.41,0:17:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太差勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.99,0:17:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.74,0:17:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能依靠這傢伙了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.41,0:17:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 還活著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.52,0:17:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.19,0:17:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,復活了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.83,0:17:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.47,0:17:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.94,0:17:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為什麼在你家啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.56,0:17:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊 你還記得你被劈成兩半了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.86,0:17:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊鬼？我感覺到了惡石的氣息…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.65,0:17:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惡石？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.71,0:17:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍羽同學是被惡石拐走了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.69,0:17:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被拐走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.12,0:17:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你 瑠璃被拐走了嗎啊鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.79,0:18:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是來問你這個的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.63,0:18:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直不知道藍羽同學在哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.72,0:18:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.54,0:18:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個氣息是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.09,0:18:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這個氣息是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.47,0:18:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈特啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.13,0:18:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈特？輝島奈特？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.97,0:18:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心一點啊鬼 他就在附近啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.90,0:18:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這傢伙 是研美的走狗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.13,0:18:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是狗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.56,0:18:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別來妨礙我！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.50,0:18:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.86,0:19:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研美先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.58,0:19:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來一時難分高下的樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.29,0:19:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.01,0:19:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來應該是由我出擊的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.49,0:19:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.49,0:19:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的SP現在正在抓捕輝島
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.00,0:19:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輝島奈特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.46,0:19:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.02,0:19:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為什麼沒發現啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.81,0:19:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他們拐走了大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.10,0:19:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.76,0:20:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得很讓人生氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.97,0:20:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人火大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.65,0:20:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惡石的氣息消失了啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.49,0:20:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 來了來了 豐滿小妞來了啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.05,0:20:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.80,0:20:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.32,0:20:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙怎樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.96,0:21:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 這下事態更嚴重了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.32,0:21:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快點把瑠璃醬從他們手中救出的話 她就很危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.00,0:21:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙恐怕是想從瑠璃醬身上提取血清
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.83,0:21:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血清？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.06,0:21:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 只要有那個的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.42,0:21:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈特就算處於惡石狀態也能保持正常理智
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.94,0:21:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過如果要持續提取那個的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.71,0:21:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙恐怕就再也不會釋放瑠璃醬了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.99,0:21:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.63,0:21:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.24,0:21:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她不在 你也很擔心自身安危吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.10,0:21:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你不用擔心自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.73,0:21:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的研究所裡也有血清
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.57,0:21:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一有什麼情況 你來我的研究所使用血清就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.13,0:21:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是藍羽同學再也回不來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.30,0:21:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.62,0:21:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以為此我們現在要竭盡全力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.22,0:21:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個東西安裝好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.62,0:21:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.66,0:22:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您指什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.50,0:22:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他身上安裝了發信器
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.01,0:22:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻準備進行追擊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.33,0:22:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.69,0:22:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍羽同學
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.08,0:22:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 我需要新的血液

